The upper combines technical satin and calf leather, while the ultra-supple rubber outsole has a wavy shape that references the design of the sneaker. This model features an adjustable velcro strap at the back and a feminine kitten heel. This model tends to run large. We recommend that you order a half-size smaller than your usual shoe size.

  • Velcro strap
  • Supple rubber outsole

  • LV Circle signature
  • Louis Vuitton signature on the strap
  • Made in Italy
